22人误食消毒片后，黄冈开了个紧急会议。
An emergency meeting was held in Wanggang after 22 people were accidentally given disinfectant tablets.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 钟煜豪据《黄冈日报》3月3日消息，3月2日，黄冈市委书记、市新冠肺炎疫情防控工作指挥部指挥长刘雪荣主持召开全市紧急视频会议，就当前全市疫情防控重点工作进行再安排再部署。
Huang Xueyong, secretary of the Huanggang Municipal Committee and commander of the Anti-SARS epidemic prevention and control work, held a city-wide emergency videoconference to re-arrange and re-arrange the city's major epidemic prevention and control efforts, the newspaper said.
刘雪荣指出，近期，黄梅县在疫情防控工作方面发生的事故给我们敲响了警钟，全市上下要吸取教训，引以为戒，举一反三，不断改进工作。
Liu pointed out that the recent Huangmei County in the work of disease prevention and control of the accident gave us a wake-up call, the whole city should learn from the lessons learned, take lessons, improve the work.
黄梅县防疫指挥部此前通报介绍，2月28日上午9时30分左右，黄梅县黄梅镇向窑村一组村民14户22人误食用于环境消毒的二氧化氯片（俗称“泡腾片”），剂量1粒/人。
Huangmei County Preventive Command had previously informed that, at around 9.30 a.m. on 28 February, a group of 14 families in Huangmei township, Huangmei County, had mistakenly eaten chlorine dioxide tablets (commonly known as "bubble wrap") for environmental disinfection in a dose of 1 tablet per person.
3月1日，央视新闻援引黄梅县黄梅镇人民政府消息，经查，2月25日，黄梅镇向各村社区发放防护物资时，均交代清楚了泡腾片的用途及使用方法，每粒泡腾片兑2公斤水，用于住户家中喷洒消毒。
On March 1, the CCTV news quoted the Huangmei County People's Government as saying that on February 25, Huangmei Township distributed protective materials to the village communities.
向窑村安排村妇女主任、会计罗晓红及网格员翟锦霞负责向各小组发放物资。
Arrangements were made for village women's director, accountant Xiaohong Zhai Jinxia and grid worker Zhai Jinxia to distribute materials to the teams.
27日15时许，罗晓红电话通知一组组长蒋建军到村委会领取一组防护物资，发放给村民，但电话中未告知蒋建军泡腾片的用途及使用方法。
At about 1500 hours on the 27th, Luo Xiaohong called a group leader Jiang Jianjun to collect a group of protective materials and distribute them to the villagers, but did not tell Jiang Jianjun what the use of the tablets would be and how they would be used.
蒋建军因在小组做防疫劝导工作，便电话通知该村志愿者蒋金雄到村委会领取。
Jiang Jianjun for the team to do vaccination advisory work, he called the village volunteers Jiang Jinxiong to collect.
于是，蒋金雄到村委会从罗晓红处将一组防护物资领走。
So Jiang Jinxiong to the village committee from Luo Xiaohong will take away a group of protective materials.
罗晓红向蒋金雄说明了泡腾片是兑水后用来消毒的，每家5粒。
Luo Xiaohong explained to Jiang Jinxiong that the effervescent tablets are used to disinfect water, 5 tablets per family.
蒋金雄在领到防护物资后，在一组村民蒋延安家中交给蒋建军。
Jiang Jinxiong after receiving protective materials, in a group of villagers Jiang Yenan home to Jiang Jianjun.
蒋金雄认为物资是蒋建军通知其从村委会领取的，应当清楚物资的用途及方法，便没有向蒋建军说明泡腾片的用途及使用方法。
Jiang Jinxiong thought that the materials were collected by Jiang Jianjun from the village committee. He should know the purpose and method of using the materials.
28日9时30分左右，黄梅县黄梅镇向窑村一组组长蒋建军带领该村志愿者余奇鳌、蒋带兵、蒋永新挨家挨户进行体温测试、登记、分发泡腾片时，蒋建军在未弄清泡腾片的用途及使用方法的情况下，自以为泡腾片是防治新冠病毒的药物，于是告知村民“每人一粒，吞服”，部分吞服了泡腾片的村民反映不适，蒋建军及时将发放的泡腾片收回。
When Jiang Jianjun led a group of volunteers from Huangmei county, Huangmei County, to lead a group of volunteers from the village, Yu Qiao, Jiang led troops, Jiang Yongxin to conduct house-to-house temperature testing, registration and distribution of bubble film.
在3月2日的会议上，刘雪荣强调，消毒消杀是阻断传播非常重要的技术手段，要科学规范地进行。
At the March 2 meeting, Liu stressed that disinfection and sterilization is a very important technical means of blocking transmission, to be carried out in a scientific and standardized manner.
要严格管理消毒药品，规范存放，正确使用，科学消毒，坚决杜绝安全隐患；要加强消毒人员的专业化规范化培训，持证上岗。
Strictly manage disinfection drugs, regulate storage, correct use, scientific disinfection, resolutely eliminate hidden dangers; strengthen professional standardized training of disinfectors, hold the post.
要高度重视院感管理，确保医务人员防护物资足额足量供应，相关医疗机构要切实履行主体责任，按照制度规范强化管理；援黄医疗队驻地必须实行全封闭管理，所有环节的服务人员必须实行筛查上岗，把工作做实做细做到位。
We must attach great importance to the management of hospital senses, ensure the adequate supply of protective materials for medical personnel, and strengthen the management of relevant medical institutions in accordance with the rules and regulations.
要加强监狱、看守所、戒毒所、养老院、福利院、精神病医院等特殊场所的防控，做好防控工作预案，搞好全员筛查，做到全封闭管理，全过程管控。
The prevention and control of prisons, detention centers, drug addiction treatment centers, nursing homes, welfare institutions, mental hospitals and other special places should be strengthened.
黄梅县防疫指挥部3月2日介绍，2日上午9时40分许，黄梅县黄梅镇向窑村又有3名村民治愈出院。
Huangmei County epidemic prevention command on March 2, about 9.40 a.m., Huangmei County, Huangmei town to the village of Yaocun Healing out of the hospital.
至此，该村误食消毒片的22名村民中，已有21人治愈出院，另外1人也已基本治愈，但由于年纪偏大且患有其他基础性疾病，为安全起见，继续留院观察治疗。
As a result, 21 of the 22 villagers who had mistakenly consumed disinfectant tablets in the village had been cured and another had been largely cured, but continued to be hospitalized for safety reasons because of their age and other basic illnesses.
本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
